rows.label: qst701105_msg0001
rows.name:
...Looking for a helmsman?
Are you serious?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm expensive, you know? Let's see...
How about 200,000G for starters?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0101
rows.name: What will you do?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0102
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: qst701105_msg0103
rows.name: Pay

rows.label: qst701105_msg0104
rows.name: Mention Arb's name

rows.label: qst701105_msg0201
rows.name: Oh, is that so? Come again sooooon♪

rows.label: qst701105_msg0301
rows.name:
Ugh, seriously!? Are you
a noble or something?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0302
rows.name:
I'll do it, I'll do it! So,
where do I need to go?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0303
rows.name:
...Yajika Harbor, right, right. By
the way, is this a case where I can't
be seen? Are you being followed?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0304
rows.name:
...Hmm, so it's not related to
that. But you're paying way too
much. Maybe you own a gold mine...

rows.label: qst701105_msg0305
rows.name:
Ah, no, no, just talking to myself.
Anyway, we'll meet at Yajika Harbor!
Thanks for your business♪

rows.label: qst701105_msg0401
rows.name:
Eh? You know the old master?
Why didn't you say so sooner!

rows.label: qst701105_msg0402
rows.name:
I'll take the helmsman job. I can't refuse
a referral from the master, and there's
probably a good reason for it, right?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0403
rows.name:
...Money? No, no, I don't need it! I haven't
sunk so low as to repay kindness with
ingratitude. So, where do I need to go?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0404
rows.name:
...Yajika Harbor, right, right. By
the way, is this a case where I can't
be seen? Are you being followed?

rows.label: qst701105_msg0405
rows.name:
...Hmm, so it's not related
to that. I guess I don't need
to be so cautious then.

rows.label: qst701105_msg0406
rows.name:
Ah, no, no, just talking to myself.
Anyway, we'll meet at Yajika Harbor!
Thanks for your business♪

rows.label: qst701105_msg0502
rows.name: Don't pay

rows.label: qst701105_msg0503
rows.name: Oh well, so you don't have it.
